OL,6,CG2003FAnna Ford, who had recently been
OL,7,Fsuffering from flu, lost her voice
OL,8,Ftwice on the One o'Clock News (BBC
OL,9,FOne).
OL,10,
OL,11,FAfter 18 minutes, she told viewers:
OL,12,F"I'm afraid my voice is really giving
OL,13,Fup today". Sophie Raworth presented the
OL,14,Fremainder of the programme.
